title: CryptoPunks Interest Rate - 12/6/2021
body:
This is a NEGATIVE CONSENT vote - if a quorum of greater than 20% is reached, the proposal will be deemed to be denied by the DAO. If no quorum is reached, the proposal will be deemed to be accepted by the DAO.

Proposal: MetaStreet DAO will set maximum interest rates at 35% for 30 day collateral agreements, 40% for 60 day collateral agreements and 45% for 90 day collateral agreements. Minimum interest rates (at 5% of Collateral Value) will be set at 8% for 30 day agreements, 10% for 60 day agreements and 12% for 90 day agreements. Maximum and minimum interest rates will be updated in 7 days on 12/13/2021.
